WEBVTT

00:14.556 --> 00:17.267
- [Soft music playing]
- [Clatters]

00:17.308 --> 00:20.186
[Doors opening]

00:34.743 --> 00:37.746
[Birds chirping]

00:55.430 --> 00:58.391
Alba: What did you do
with his clothes?

00:58.433 --> 01:00.477
- I burned them.
Most of them.

01:01.644 --> 01:03.104
Alba: What is this?

01:06.900 --> 01:08.360
Batty: I don't know.

01:09.569 --> 01:13.239
Alba: Make sure to sand it
down, it looks dreadful.

01:13.281 --> 01:14.491
Make the bed first.

01:20.246 --> 01:22.123
And bring me a lamp
from the living room.

01:22.165 --> 01:24.125
I need light.

01:25.627 --> 01:27.253
And then run me a bath.

01:31.841 --> 01:33.385
[***]

01:33.426 --> 01:34.803
Can you cook?

01:34.844 --> 01:36.596
- A little. I like to.

01:36.638 --> 01:38.181
- What can you cook?

01:39.683 --> 01:41.393
- Fish soup.

01:41.434 --> 01:42.894
Omelette.

01:42.936 --> 01:43.895
Roast chicken.

01:43.937 --> 01:44.979
Eggplant caponata.

01:48.858 --> 01:50.151
- That's it?

01:51.945 --> 01:53.488
- Avocado toast?

01:56.741 --> 01:58.702
- I like Indian.

01:58.743 --> 02:00.704
Palak paneer, biryani.

02:00.745 --> 02:02.455
Korma.

02:02.497 --> 02:03.456
Learn.

02:09.587 --> 02:11.506
[Footsteps receding]

02:21.683 --> 02:22.642
Mm- hm.

02:26.563 --> 02:28.314
[Water splashes]

02:33.570 --> 02:36.531
[***]

02:55.592 --> 02:58.345
[Voice- over] At first,
ruling over someone

02:58.386 --> 03:00.221
feels perfectly natural.

03:09.814 --> 03:10.732
Batty: Thank you.

03:12.609 --> 03:14.319
For not turning me in.

03:14.361 --> 03:16.446
I don't deserve it.

03:16.488 --> 03:17.405
Thank you.

03:19.282 --> 03:21.534
Thank you for letting me live.

03:21.576 --> 03:23.328
Thank you.

03:23.370 --> 03:26.414
[***]

03:36.966 --> 03:40.261
[***]

03:47.769 --> 03:49.020
Alba: Did you poison it?

03:49.062 --> 03:50.271
Batty: No.

03:50.313 --> 03:51.940
Alba: Which one is mine?

03:51.981 --> 03:53.316
Drink it.

03:55.318 --> 03:56.569
You have 30 seconds.

04:09.874 --> 04:12.627
Now drink yours.
In one fell swoop.

04:32.022 --> 04:35.400
[Sighs] I want to be alone.

04:35.442 --> 04:37.110
Go swim in the ocean.

04:37.152 --> 04:38.778
I'll watch you from here.

04:38.820 --> 04:40.071
Try not to drown.

04:40.113 --> 04:41.072
It would be so suspicious,

04:41.114 --> 04:42.532
it would probably
get me arrested,

04:42.574 --> 04:46.703
but you'd be dead,
so you couldn't enjoy it.

04:56.921 --> 04:58.673
[Sighs]

04:58.715 --> 05:01.676
[***]

05:09.851 --> 05:12.729
[Waves splashing]

05:14.397 --> 05:17.525
[***]

05:56.773 --> 06:00.443
[Birds chirping]

06:15.875 --> 06:18.586
[Water running]

06:21.006 --> 06:24.676
[Birds chirping]

06:34.686 --> 06:36.771
[Voice- over]
Cruelty is underrated.

06:36.813 --> 06:38.732
It's surprisingly easy
to order people around

06:38.773 --> 06:41.234
and make them do
ridiculous things,

06:41.276 --> 06:44.195
particularly monsters
who steal your husband,

06:44.237 --> 06:47.532
your house,
and your entire identity.

06:47.574 --> 06:48.950
- You have lovely hair.

06:53.288 --> 06:54.873
[***]

06:54.914 --> 06:57.792
[Water running]

07:00.962 --> 07:02.714
[Gas stove clicks]

07:04.716 --> 07:07.635
[Chopping]

07:17.854 --> 07:20.648
[Cutlery clinks]

07:57.894 --> 07:59.187
Do you like it?

07:59.229 --> 08:01.147
- No.

08:01.189 --> 08:03.525
- What can I do better?

08:03.566 --> 08:05.652
- I can write
a whole book about that.

08:05.694 --> 08:06.903
- That's not
very constructive.

08:24.170 --> 08:25.380
Alba: Put this on.

08:27.757 --> 08:29.050
Over your eyes.

08:45.775 --> 08:47.318
Are you dizzy?
- Yes.

08:53.199 --> 08:54.284
- Are you dizzier?

08:54.325 --> 08:55.326
Batty: Yes.

08:56.411 --> 08:58.371
[Footsteps]

08:58.413 --> 08:59.414
[Chair slides]

08:59.456 --> 09:00.832
Alba: Follow the sound
of my voice.

09:00.874 --> 09:04.127
[Footsteps]

09:05.128 --> 09:06.046
[Chair thuds]

09:06.087 --> 09:07.213
Come to me.

09:16.222 --> 09:17.432
[Glass shatters]

09:20.226 --> 09:21.478
Are you afraid?

09:25.440 --> 09:27.108
Are you afraid?

09:28.360 --> 09:29.277
- Yes.

09:32.030 --> 09:32.989
- Come to me.

09:33.031 --> 09:36.117
[Footsteps]

09:38.828 --> 09:41.206
[Chair clatters]

09:41.247 --> 09:42.832
Did I say stop?

09:44.626 --> 09:46.169
[Loud thud]

09:47.212 --> 09:50.465
[Batty shaking]

09:52.967 --> 09:53.927
- Settle down, Batty.

09:56.971 --> 09:58.181
There's no need to shake.

10:02.102 --> 10:05.063
You do not have
permission to shake.

10:05.105 --> 10:08.274
[Batty breathing heavily]

10:17.492 --> 10:19.160
- Mm- hm.

10:19.202 --> 10:22.497
[Batty breathing heavily]

10:24.374 --> 10:25.333
- Good.

10:27.669 --> 10:30.839
Now come to me.

10:30.880 --> 10:33.550
[Batty breathing heavily]

10:45.437 --> 10:46.521
Alba: Stop.

10:52.110 --> 10:53.570
Take one step backwards.

10:57.323 --> 10:59.200
Down on your knees.

11:04.122 --> 11:05.457
Crawl to me.

11:07.334 --> 11:10.295
[Tense music playing]
[Batty breathing heavily]

11:53.088 --> 11:54.339
- Well done.

12:02.222 --> 12:05.225
[Crickets chirping]
[Water dripping]

12:17.278 --> 12:20.281
[Water dripping]

12:26.621 --> 12:27.914
[Squeaking]

13:02.615 --> 13:05.493
[Water dripping]

13:11.332 --> 13:13.585
[Exhales]

13:13.626 --> 13:16.463
[Voice- over] It helped
when she fought back.

13:16.504 --> 13:19.341
It felt like validation.

13:19.382 --> 13:20.967
I was on the right track.

13:22.302 --> 13:24.054
- How did you sleep?

13:24.095 --> 13:25.013
- Fine.

13:26.514 --> 13:27.474
You?

13:28.558 --> 13:29.517
- Fine.

13:59.339 --> 14:01.383
- I know you love
your cold milk.

14:04.594 --> 14:05.679
Lap it up.

14:11.059 --> 14:13.520
[Soft dramatic music playing]

14:49.514 --> 14:52.475
[Wind blowing]

14:56.312 --> 14:59.482
[Birds chirping]

15:06.865 --> 15:08.783
Did you know about me
when you met Archie?

15:11.745 --> 15:13.204
- Yes.

15:14.122 --> 15:16.416
- You said he told you
it was over between us.

15:18.126 --> 15:19.544
- But he didn't say that.

15:20.587 --> 15:21.796
- What did he say exactly?

15:29.471 --> 15:31.097
- He said you were
a capricious child

15:31.139 --> 15:33.850
with zero interest in him,

15:33.892 --> 15:38.104
a narcissist who took pictures
of yourself all day.

15:38.146 --> 15:40.857
That making love had become
merely copulation,

15:40.899 --> 15:43.693
the most unimaginative
activity on earth.

15:46.279 --> 15:47.489
That he was suffocating.

15:50.450 --> 15:51.576
- Oh.

15:54.788 --> 15:57.540
[Voice- over] But slowly,
the conundrum of repetition

15:57.582 --> 16:00.335
begins to weigh on you.

16:00.377 --> 16:01.753
You have to keep
upping the stakes

16:01.795 --> 16:04.756
and it becomes
a lot like a job

16:04.798 --> 16:06.758
like the poor souls
who work at the post office

16:06.800 --> 16:08.218
and go ballistic because

16:08.259 --> 16:10.887
the mail simply keeps on coming.

16:10.929 --> 16:12.430
- Would you like
anything else?

16:14.849 --> 16:16.184
- Sing.

16:18.603 --> 16:20.647
Yes, little monkey.
Sing.

16:25.860 --> 16:29.197
[Footsteps]

16:40.333 --> 16:46.339
- * Seems like you were
In a glass hotel *

16:47.757 --> 16:49.426
* Seems like *

16:51.636 --> 16:53.346
* Seems like *

16:55.557 --> 16:59.352
* Seems like there was
Someone else as well *

17:01.229 --> 17:02.689
* Seems like *

17:04.566 --> 17:07.610
* Seems *

17:13.324 --> 17:17.370
* Seems like you were
in your glass hotel *

17:18.913 --> 17:20.540
* Seems like *

17:22.584 --> 17:24.210
* Seems like *

17:25.670 --> 17:29.341
* It seems like
Everything was going well *

17:30.383 --> 17:36.389
* It seems like a dream *

17:39.684 --> 17:42.771
* Well the radio was playing *

17:42.812 --> 17:45.357
* In the darkness
of the hall *

17:46.358 --> 17:48.860
* There was someone
Standing with you *

17:48.902 --> 17:52.781
* Who just wasn't there at all *

17:52.822 --> 17:56.409
* And you were laughing *

18:02.290 --> 18:04.626
* Well the telephone
was ringing *

18:06.086 --> 18:08.505
* In a corridor of blue *

18:11.299 --> 18:16.429
* A geranium came out of it
Reminded me of you *

18:17.597 --> 18:21.601
* And I was crying *

18:26.981 --> 18:31.277
* Seems like you were
In a glass hotel *

18:32.070 --> 18:37.409
* Seems like, it seems like *

18:37.450 --> 18:41.955
* Seems like there was
Someone else as well *

18:41.996 --> 18:48.670
* It seems like it seems *

18:50.547 --> 18:53.383
* Well, there's nothing
In the future *

18:53.425 --> 18:55.927
* And there's nothing
In the past *

18:55.969 --> 18:58.054
* There is only
This one moment *

18:58.096 --> 19:01.683
* And you've
Got to make it last *

19:01.725 --> 19:07.313
* And you were laughing *

19:07.355 --> 19:16.031
In a glass hotel *

19:40.138 --> 19:42.349
[***]

19:42.390 --> 19:45.518
Alba: [Voice- over] I thought
about her day and night.

19:49.147 --> 19:51.816
I considered her my friend.

19:51.858 --> 19:52.901
[Waves splashing]

19:52.942 --> 19:55.779
Well, not a friend.

19:55.820 --> 19:57.072
Not exactly.

19:58.198 --> 20:01.743
I was in a state of...
confusion.

20:04.829 --> 20:06.706
I dreamt about her constantly.

20:11.670 --> 20:14.547
[Waves splashing]

20:19.052 --> 20:22.514
[***]

21:11.146 --> 21:12.939
How did it happen?

21:12.981 --> 21:15.859
- It's the heat.

21:15.900 --> 21:17.152
- Where are your clothes?

21:22.574 --> 21:24.826
This is so embarrassing.
Wear this.

21:24.868 --> 21:26.703
[Gasps]

21:26.745 --> 21:29.581
[Breathes deeply]

21:35.045 --> 21:36.087
[Voice- over] It became clear

21:36.129 --> 21:38.923
I had to bring the game
to a stop.

21:38.965 --> 21:41.801
So I set a trap.

21:41.843 --> 21:45.472
I would demand something
she couldn't possibly submit to.

21:46.848 --> 21:48.767
I have devised a game.

21:49.768 --> 21:51.770
I hope you will have
as much fun playing it

21:51.811 --> 21:54.105
as I had devising it.

21:54.147 --> 21:55.482
Have you noticed
the construction site

21:55.523 --> 21:56.941
across from the market?

21:56.983 --> 21:57.942
- Yes.

21:58.985 --> 22:00.779
- You will go there.

22:00.820 --> 22:03.865
You will pay three workers
500 dollars apiece

22:03.907 --> 22:05.617
to come home with you.

22:05.658 --> 22:10.038
The biggest, meanest,
roughest ones.

22:10.080 --> 22:14.501
You will fuck all three of them
here in front of me.

22:20.090 --> 22:21.758
- What if they don't
speak English?

22:23.760 --> 22:26.137
- Repeat after me:
Boys.

22:26.179 --> 22:27.597
- Boys.

22:27.639 --> 22:31.059
- I need you to fill
all my holes.

22:31.101 --> 22:34.062
- I need you to fill
all my eggs.

22:34.104 --> 22:35.188
- Holes.

22:35.230 --> 22:36.523
- Holes.

22:36.564 --> 22:39.859
- Means "holes".
Huevos means "eggs".

22:41.861 --> 22:42.821
- Oh.

22:44.948 --> 22:45.949
- Go on.

22:45.990 --> 22:48.785
[Soft emotional music]

22:55.000 --> 22:57.794
[Receding footsteps]

23:23.069 --> 23:26.573
[Soft emotional music]

23:49.721 --> 23:51.598
[Voice-over]
What if you met someone

23:51.639 --> 23:53.850
willing to do
anything you ask of them.

24:01.649 --> 24:02.859
Anything at all.

24:04.861 --> 24:09.866
[***]

24:16.331 --> 24:21.336
[***]

24:28.343 --> 24:35.350
[***]

24:36.976 --> 24:37.977
Stop.

24:41.022 --> 24:42.107
Stop.

25:08.925 --> 25:10.468
I'm so sorry.

25:10.510 --> 25:12.512
So terribly sorry.

25:20.186 --> 25:21.938
I don't know why I did that.

25:21.980 --> 25:23.106
This is not who I am.

25:23.148 --> 25:26.234
[Water running]

25:30.989 --> 25:34.409
Please forgive me.

25:36.161 --> 25:38.163
- Maybe we're not
who we think we are.

25:40.081 --> 25:42.167
- I'm so sorry.

25:42.208 --> 25:44.419
- Maybe everybody thinks
they're someone they're not.

25:46.087 --> 25:47.505
- Can I ask you a question?

25:48.965 --> 25:50.300
- I don't know.

25:50.342 --> 25:52.218
- Can I ask you a question?

25:53.345 --> 25:54.429
- I guess.

25:56.306 --> 25:58.183
- Do you ever say
what you mean?

25:59.642 --> 26:02.270
- Not very often.
You?

26:03.438 --> 26:06.316
- Do you like
to be told what to do?

26:06.358 --> 26:08.485
- Is this another game?

26:08.526 --> 26:09.444
- No.

26:11.029 --> 26:12.530
- Is this another game?

26:15.116 --> 26:18.244
[Water running]

26:20.205 --> 26:21.331
[Tap squeaks]

26:22.999 --> 26:26.252
[***]

26:36.221 --> 26:39.307
[Waves splashing]

26:41.601 --> 26:43.019
[Crickets chirping]

26:43.061 --> 26:44.229
[Knocks on door]

26:45.605 --> 26:46.648
- Come in.

26:46.690 --> 26:48.274
[Door opens]

26:52.404 --> 26:54.280
- Just wanted
to say good night.

26:55.198 --> 26:56.324
- Good night.

27:01.162 --> 27:03.248
Do you want to
sleep here with me?

27:05.959 --> 27:07.293
- No.

27:09.421 --> 27:11.589
- You could move into
this room for a little bit.

27:14.217 --> 27:15.301
- Thank you.

27:16.636 --> 27:17.929
I appreciate it.

27:22.976 --> 27:24.477
[Door closes]

27:24.519 --> 27:25.437
- [Sighs]

27:27.397 --> 27:30.483
[Crickets chirping]

27:32.110 --> 27:33.069
[Distant flogging]

27:33.111 --> 27:34.237
[Gasps]

27:38.450 --> 27:41.536
[Footsteps thudding on stairs]

27:43.288 --> 27:46.332
[Flogging]

27:59.304 --> 28:02.307
Batty! Batty?

28:02.349 --> 28:03.725
Stop that right now.

28:03.767 --> 28:05.352
Batty!

28:05.393 --> 28:06.686
Please don't do this.

28:07.771 --> 28:09.439
[Drawer opens]

28:12.108 --> 28:14.277
Stop! Right! Now!

28:15.779 --> 28:16.988
What are you doing?

28:18.031 --> 28:19.115
- Let me go.

28:19.157 --> 28:21.993
[Alba shushing]

28:25.163 --> 28:26.664
- Tell me what to do.

28:26.706 --> 28:28.625
Please tell me what to do.

28:28.667 --> 28:31.461
[Panting]

28:46.267 --> 28:47.602
- Where did you find a Bible?

28:51.272 --> 28:53.316
Where did you find this?

28:53.358 --> 28:55.360
Did Inocencia leave this here?

28:57.821 --> 28:59.364
[Bible thuds]

29:05.203 --> 29:06.705
- It makes no sense.

29:09.165 --> 29:11.251
It makes perfect sense.

29:11.292 --> 29:14.504
[Panting]

29:17.090 --> 29:19.300
[Cries]

29:24.097 --> 29:25.515
[Door opens]

29:36.568 --> 29:37.736
[Light switch clicking]

29:49.789 --> 29:52.334
[Water running]

29:56.880 --> 29:58.089
[Door creaks]

30:00.550 --> 30:03.595
[Soft music playing]

30:32.248 --> 30:35.794
[Soft kisses]

30:49.557 --> 30:50.809
[Light switch clicks]

30:52.936 --> 30:58.149
[***]

31:25.885 --> 31:30.890
[***]

32:00.920 --> 32:05.925
[***]

32:25.945 --> 32:30.950
[***]

32:46.424 --> 32:51.429
[***]

